msgstr ""
"Support for third-party \"custom\" events, including those arising in "
"custom modules."

#: ../../general/process/process_bpmn/process_bpmn_ecos_events_integrations.rst:20
msgid ""
"При реакции на события должна быть возможность получить информацию о "
"событии и настраивать дополнительную модель на основе Records API."
msgstr ""
"When reacting to events, it must be possible to obtain information about "
"the event and configure an additional model based on the Records API."

#: ../../general/process/process_bpmn/process_bpmn_ecos_events_integrations.rst:21
msgid ""
